'''''Vendetta''''' was the name of four starships:
*a [[Dreadnaught-class heavy cruiser/Legends|''Dreadnaught''-class heavy cruiser]] under Ambassador [[Furgan]]'s command, see [[Vendetta (Dreadnaught-class)]]
*an [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Starfleet]], see [[Vendetta (Imperial-class)/Legends|Vendetta (Imperial-class)]]
*[[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor's]] personal [[Starship/Legends|starship]] of unknown make, see [[Vendetta (Xizor)]]
*an ''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer in ''[[LEGO Star Wars]]'', see [[Vendetta (Freemarker Adventures)]]
